dict.string: Must be sorted to use. Picks an element in the middle of the set, if the element is greater than the desired element, remove the upper half. Repeat.
A general purpose algorithm (metaheuristic) that's used in DFS to exhaust one path completely before returning to the root.
Checks each branch from the current node, before attending to the left most branch of the root node.
Implements backtracking to exhaust one route completely before returning to the previous node.
A heuristic used to linearly check every element.
